---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Surgical Techniques – DGIS Fortaleza 2026" lang="en">
<div class="sec-dark" style="padding:52px 24px 48px;">
  <div class="container" style="padding:0;">
    <span class="eyebrow-white">Surgical protocols</span>
    <h1 class="page-h1-white" style="margin-top:10px;">3 Digital Guided Surgery Techniques</h1>
    <div class="gold-bar"></div>
    <p class="lead-white" style="max-width:600px;">From basic to advanced in a single week. Three complete protocols on real patients.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="sec-white">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="grid-2" style="gap:48px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:64px;padding-bottom:64px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--sky100);">
      <div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span class="badge-basic" style="font-size:.75rem;padding:4px 12px;">Basic–Intermediate level</span><span style="font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--sl400);">Days 1–2 · Mon–Tue</span></div>
        <h2 class="sec-h2">Digital Guided Implantology</h2>
        <div class="sky-bar"></div>
        <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom:16px;">The standard computer-guided surgery protocol. 3D preoperative planning with surgical guide design software, guided execution with maximum precision.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px;">
          {['3D digital case planning in software','Design and fabrication of surgical guide','Implant placement with digital guide','Postoperative planned vs. executed verification'].map(i=>(
            <li style="display:flex;gap:10px;font-size:.86rem;color:var(--sl700);word-wrap:break-word;"><svg width="16" height="16" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>{i}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/en/registration" class="btn btn-sky">Apply now →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="img-frame"><img src="/pptx_images/image6.jpeg" alt="Guided implantology" style="height:320px;width:100%;object-fit:cover;" /><div class="img-cap">Surgical guides in mouth — digital guided implantology</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-2" style="gap:48px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:64px;padding-bottom:64px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--sky100);">
      <div class="img-frame"><img src="/pptx_images/image9.jpeg" alt="OneDay OnePiece" style="height:320px;width:100%;object-fit:cover;" /><div class="img-cap">OneDay OnePiece implant — immediate loading</div></div>
      <div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span class="badge-mid" style="font-size:.75rem;padding:4px 12px;">Intermediate level</span><span style="font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--sl400);">Day 3 · Wednesday</span></div>
        <h2 class="sec-h2">OneDay OnePiece</h2>
        <div class="sky-bar"></div>
        <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom:16px;">Immediate loading protocol with one-piece implants. The patient arrives and leaves the same day with a provisional crown placed. Maximum clinical efficiency with immediate aesthetic result.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px;">
          {['Selection of cases suitable for immediate loading','OneDay-specific digital planning','Guided surgery with one-piece implant','Provisional loading on the same day as surgery'].map(i=>(
            <li style="display:flex;gap:10px;font-size:.86rem;color:var(--sl700);word-wrap:break-word;"><svg width="16" height="16" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;" fill="none" stroke="var(--sky500)" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>{i}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/en/registration" class="btn btn-sky">Apply now →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-2" style="gap:48px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:56px;">
      <div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span class="badge-advanced" style="font-size:.75rem;padding:4px 12px;">Advanced level</span><span style="font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--sl400);">Days 4–5 · Thu–Fri</span></div>
        <h2 class="sec-h2">All-on-Four</h2>
        <div class="sky-bar"></div>
        <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom:16px;">Full arch rehabilitation with four strategically placed implants using digital guidance. The most complex protocol of the programme, with advanced planning and complete arch outcome.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px;">
          {['Advanced full-arch planning','Distal angulation of posterior implants','All-on-Four surgery with digital guide','Immediate loading with full provisional prosthesis'].map(i=>(
            <li style="display:flex;gap:10px;font-size:.86rem;color:var(--sl700);word-wrap:break-word;"><svg width="16" height="16" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;" fill="none" stroke="#6d28d9" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>{i}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/en/registration" class="btn btn-sky">Apply now →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="img-frame"><img src="/pptx_images/image8.jpeg" alt="All-on-Four surgery" style="height:320px;width:100%;object-fit:cover;" /><div class="img-cap">All-on-Four team surgery — CliniCare Training</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-banner"><div><h3 style="font-weight:800;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--sky900);margin-bottom:6px;">Three techniques. One week. Real patients.</h3><p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--sl500);">You operate in every case under direct expert supervision.</p></div><a href="/en/registration" class="btn btn-sky btn-lg">Apply now →</a></div>
  </div>
</div>
</Layout>
